entries.journal_entry_description: Your newly acquired rank within the RSF will allow you to access confidential information within the RSF mainframe. Find out what you can about the Old Republic droid modules.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Use the RSF computer to access the information it holds about Old Republic droid modules.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: I understand that you've finally achieved the clearance level you need. Very well then, go to the RSF mainframe and learn what it knows about the Old Republic droid modules.
